- Validation + error accumulation with fp-ts: [fp-ts validation skill](../../skills/fp-ts-validation/SKILL.md).
- Error channel patterns: [fp-ts errors skill](../../skills/fp-ts-errors/SKILL.md).

## Enforcement

- **Detect**: `any` / untyped `@Body()`; repository classes in misnamed files; Zod schemas defined inside `/domain` (move to boundary DTO modules).
- **Fix**: Add Zod schema + `safeParse`; rename infra files to include technology prefix; keep DTO types next to controllers or `infrastructure/http/dto/`.
